column5: Going to Lac Seul in June and would love to hear from anybody who can help me with presentations that work for Smallmouth on Lac Seul.

Cast small lures into rocky shore lines. You'll catch northeran and eyes at same time. Hot spots are in the shade of rock, stump,etc. Many, Many Bass on east end of Lac Suel, I assume same on Ear Falls end. Warning grind barbs off. (Learned hard way.)
